OL,3,CMan jailed for murder he committed two
OL,4,Cdays after prison release
OL,6,FA man who stabbed a retired carer to
OL,7,Fdeath just two days after he was
OL,8,Freleased from prison has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor life.
OL,11,FOwen Blades, 27, killed John Connolly,
OL,12,F69, at his house in Portland Street,
OL,13,FLincoln in 13 June 2024. He was
OL,14,Fstabbed 18 times including a fatal
OL,15,Fblow to the neck.
OL,17,FMr Connolly's body was found five days
OL,18,Flater by family members.
OL,20,FBlades pleaded guilty in January.
