OL,3,CMan jailed for murder he committed two
OL,4,Cdays after prison release
OL,6,FThe court heard he had been released
OL,7,Ffrom HMP Lincoln on 11 June after
OL,8,Fserving a sentence for assault.
OL,10,FOn the day of the murder, Blades,
OL,11,Fassaulted another man, brought a knife
OL,12,Fout in public, and carried out a
OL,13,Fburglary and another theft.
OL,15,FHe was charged with a GBH which had
OL,16,Ftaken place at Merkur Slots in Lincoln
OL,17,Fthat same day. He was on remand when
OL,18,Fthe force's investigation started and
OL,19,Fhe was quickly identified as a suspect.
