OL,3,CMan jailed for murder he committed two
OL,4,Cdays after prison release
OL,6,FBlades also pleaded guilty to a
OL,7,Fburglary, possession of a knife in
OL,8,Fpublic place, and theft of food from
OL,9,FTesco.
OL,11,FLincolnshire Police said Blades was a
OL,12,Fstranger, and "there was no reason for
OL,13,Fhim to target John."
OL,15,FIn a statement following the
OL,16,Fsentencing, his family said he was
OL,17,F"deeply loved" and he should have been
OL,18,Fsafe in his own home.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
