OL,3,CMan jailed for murder he committed two
OL,4,Cdays after prison release
OL,6,F"This has left the biggest hole in our
OL,7,Fhearts that will never be filled."
OL,9,FDetective Chief Inspector Jen Lovatt
OL,10,Fsaid Blades knew what he had done
OL,11,Fwhile sitting in a prison cell for an
OL,12,Fearlier assault.
OL,14,F"Blades knew what he had done. He knew
OL,15,Fthat he had stabbed and killed John on
OL,16,F13 June, but sat in his prison cell
OL,17,Fafter having been swiftly arrested for
OL,18,Fan assault that same day, and said
OL,19,Fnothing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
