OL,3,CMan jailed for murder he committed two
OL,4,Cdays after prison release
OL,6,F"We also need to think about the other
OL,7,Fvictims of Blades' crimes, who will
OL,8,Fhave also been traumatised by his
OL,9,Factions."
OL,11,FOwen Blades was sentenced to 32 years
OL,12,Fand 3 months for murder.
OL,14,FHe also received a sentence of six
OL,15,Fyears and nine months for GBH at
OL,16,FMerkur Slots, two years for the
OL,17,Faggravated burglary, two months for
OL,18,Fthe theft from Tesco, and two years
OL,19,Fand three months for possession of a
OL,20,Foffensive weapon.
